messages.text: almost at the intersection of Lancaster and Rose
sorry. I know… I was gonna miss curfew…
Why were you going to be late?
just hanging wit some friends. Lost track of the time
You mean you were with Kate.
I’m not stupid. I know she lives out that way.
fine. yes. I was, can you just come help me.
You lied to me about where you were. And you weren’t going to make curfew.
so that means you’re not gonna help me?
You have to learn to take responsibility for your actions and suffer the consequences.
I won’t be there to look after you anymore and make sure you’re home on time and doing the right thing.
i don’t need a lecture right now. I just need to get home
we can talk about this later. Can you just come get me
Like I said.  You have to learn from your OWN mistakes.
this isn’t some karma thing.  My cars broken!!
You’re going to have to figure it out.
it’s almost freakin 12 and I’m stranded in basically the middle of nowhere.
it’s cold, rainy and pitch black and my hood is smoking.
Well, you should’ve been home on time.  Call a tow truck.
ha. Like they’re is open at this hour
i could be eaten by a bear or bobcat or somethin
you don’t know. I’m by the freakin woods
but whatever. You probably don’t care anyway
Stay calm son. Open the hood.
i’m not opening that thing. It’s smoking bad
plus I’m stayin in my car. Too dark out there.
Come on. You’ll be fine.  Part of being a man is doing things like this.
you’ve got to be kidding…So now you wanna make a lesson out of this
Just open the hood and tell me what’s going on inside. I’ll help guide you if it’s fixable.
Get out of the car and open the hood.  You have to learn.
you’re sick. This is all one large lesson to you. Bet you’re smiling real big right now
i have to get home somehow
I’ll come get you.  If it’s not fixable.
i’m gonna message mom. She’s always had more sense then you
Lancaster, about to hit Rose. That back road
Oh my… Lancaster. Is that where they’ve been having all the disappearances??
did you not read what she said??!?!
It’s fine.  Get out of the car and lift the hood.
mom can you please come get me
No.  You need to check and see if you can fix it first.
Can we just go get him??
No! He was going to be late and he lied to us about where he was at.
Because of this, he needs to learn to take responsibility for his actions.
but this has NOTHING to do with my car breaking down
freakin punish me when I get home. Just come get me now
Listen to me.  If you want help, let us help you.
i’ll never forgive you for this
Get out and check under the hood.  Tell me what you see.
i hope it blows up. Be happy then?
can’t freakin see anything will all the smoke
Was it acting funny before it broke down?
yeah, it made this weird rattling sound as I was driving
How long has it been doing that?
A week?! And you didn’t tell us?
See if you can flag them down.
should I flag them down or no
Did they say they can help?
yeah, he’s looking under the hood right now
says the carburetor needs more water
says he has to go home to get some water
idk, he didn’t give me an exact address or anything. Said he’d be back in 10 min
like to see him fix it first
You didn’t introduce yourself? Shake his hand?
You’re going to be grounded from your car after this.
I thought that man was fixing it?
i guess, I just don’t feel safe
i just have a bad feeling.  Feels like someone is watching me
For Christ’s sake, go get him!!
I see his car.  It’s still smoking.
Wait, I see a car coming.
Maybe it’s that guy who was helping.
Robert. Answer us if you’re out there.
If you would’ve just gone and gotten him!!!
